---
// Mission.astro — BhummiVastu mission section
// Displays the Purusha Sukta shloka, its translation, and the
// connection to Vastu & Astrology practice.

interface Props {
  id?: string;
}
const { id } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  class="relative not-prose py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 via-orange-50 to-yellow-50 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 overflow-hidden"
  {...id ? { id } : {}}
>
  <!-- Decorative square frames -->
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-16 -right-16 w-80 h-80 border-[32px] border-amber-200/30 dark:border-amber-900/20 rotate-12"
  ></div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-56 h-56 border-[16px] border-orange-200/20 dark:border-orange-900/15 rotate-6"
  ></div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 w-72 h-72 border-[28px] border-orange-200/30 dark:border-orange-900/20 -rotate-12"
  ></div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-48 h-48 border-[14px] border-amber-200/20 dark:border-amber-900/15 -rotate-6"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">

    <!-- Section label -->
    <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mb-6 letter-spacing-widest">
      Our Mission &amp; Philosophy
    </p>

    <!-- Sanskrit shloka -->
    <blockquote class="mb-6">
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-amber-100 tracking-wide">
        सहस्रशीर्षा पुरुषः सहस्राक्षः सहस्रपात्‌।<br />
        स भूमिं विश्वतो वृत्वाऽत्यतिष्ठद्दशाङ्गुलम्‌॥
      </p>
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-amber-100 tracking-wide mt-4">
        पुरुष एवेदं सर्वं यद्भूतं यच्च भव्यम्‌।<br />
        उतामृतत्वस्येशानो यदन्नेनातिरोहति॥
      </p>
      <footer class="mt-3 text-xs text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-500 font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
        — Purusha Sūkta, Rigveda 10.90
      </footer>
    </blockquote>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="h-px w-16 bg-amber-400/60"></div>
      <span class="text-amber-500 text-xl" aria-hidden="true">✦</span>
      <div class="h-px w-16 bg-amber-400/60"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- English translation -->
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300 italic leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
      "That Infinite Being has a thousand heads, a thousand eyes and a thousand feet enveloping the whole universe on all sides. He exists beyond ten fingers. — that which is, that which was, and that which is yet to be, is nothing but this Infinite Being. He remains the lord of immortality."
    </p>

    <!-- Contextual bridge to Vastu & Astrology -->
    <div class="bg-white/70 dark:bg-slate-800/60 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-900/50 rounded-2xl px-6 py-6 md:py-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        Vastu Shastra is the ancient science of <strong class="text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400">aligning physical space with this infinite cosmic order</strong> — ensuring that every room, every direction, every threshold resonates with the natural flow of energy that pervades all existence.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        Vedic Astrology charts the same cosmic intelligence as it moves through time — revealing the patterns that shape health, relationships, and prosperity in our lives.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 leading-relaxed">
        At BhummiVastu, we bridge these two timeless sciences to help seekers across India live in conscious harmony with the universe around them.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
